27:55.264 --> 27:56.842
- Come on. 
- They look good to me.

27:56.985 --> 27:58.030
- Good, not great? 
- Lorelai.

27:58.152 --> 27:58.879
Twenty-eight to go.

27:59.023 --> 28:01.614
Does it bother you that the word "laundry" is misspelled?

28:01.746 --> 28:05.521
No! I proofed these pages a million times.

28:05.627 --> 28:09.785
That breaks my heart. L-a-u-n-d-r-y. That's right.

28:09.889 --> 28:13.350
- No, it's d-r-i-e. 
