30:25.286 --> 30:27.587
You left me hanging with the Lords of Flatbush here.

30:27.745 --> 30:28.345
Sorry.

30:31.775 --> 30:34.274
- Aren't you gonna sit? 
- He doesn't want to make a lap.

30:34.420 --> 30:35.784
- A lap is an illusion. 
- What?

30:35.907 --> 30:38.257
- Don't get him started. 
